{"word":"δέω","slug":"δέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>δέω</el></b> [not to be confused with the homograph <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δέω\">δέω</a></el> ‘lack, stand in need of’, with which the impersonal <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δεῖ\">δεῖ</a></el> is associated] <b><i>bind</i><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> of physical restraint <b><a href='B:470 12:29'>Mt 12:29</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a>; by extension <b><a href='B:490 13:16'>Lk 13:16</a>; <a href='B:510 20:22'>Ac 20:22</a>; <a href='B:520 7:2'>Ro 7:2</a>; <a href='B:530 7:27'>1 Cor 7:27</a>; <a href='B:620 2:9'>2 Ti 2:9</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> as legal term <i>forbid</i> <b><a href='B:470 16:19'>Mt 16:19</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ opp.\">opp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:λύω\">λύω</a></el>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <a href='B:490 13:15'>Lk 13:15f</a>)<b>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:δέχομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:δή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}